Title: VAMPA
Description: Legendary female DJ VAMPA headlining a show at Adelaide Hall in Toronto. VAMPA is a bona fide genre-bender. Her ability to layer her signature delicate melodies over pounding synths evokes the sensation of swirling darkness and light together. Her energy is unmistakable — VAMPA has come to break our necks and suck our blood.

Title: We Hate YOOKiE
Description: DJ duo YOOKiE, comprised of twin brothers Anthony and Chris Alfaro, performing in Ottawa at Escapade Music Festival. The duo is famous for having the crowd scream "F*** YOOKiE" during their live sets.
